* This tool is a custom traffic generator that transmits UDP packets in form of a speed test.  
* The tool requires 5 input parameters:
* Duration Of Run (minimum 15 seconds), Destination IP (A.B.C.D), Average Bit Rate (minimum 10 Mbps), 
* Packet Size ( > 1200 Bytes; max 1500 bytes), UDP Port Number (default =9; if 0 then set to 9).
* Tested on OSX 10.14.6 and Ubuntu-18.04 LTS

/****************************************************************************************************************




